Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:41.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:52.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:59.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:06.91,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:13.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:17.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:27.76,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:34.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:41.21,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:52.69,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:03:00.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:41.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在傷害別人之前　不必強顏歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:52.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說著她低下頭　在黑夜裡哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:59.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷黏合在一起　渾身僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:06.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下個不停　卻沒有傘來遮擋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:13.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己囚禁在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:17.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戰鬥才能求生的因果之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心　我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:27.76,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的彼岸所見到的　是五彩光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:34.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的窗口　映照出那時蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:41.21,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　雖說不能像鳥兒一樣自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:52.69,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害別人之後的那份心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:03:00.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕地閉上眼　哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:58.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}なくす事が拾うためなら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:04.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}別れるのは出逢うため
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:09.55,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}「さようなら」のあとには　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:15.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}「こんにちは」と出逢うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:26.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}緑色芝生に寝ころんでいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:37.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}動物も一緒にゴロゴロしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:45.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}今日は良い事がたくさんあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:58.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}若丟棄是為了撿回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:04.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}那分別就是為了相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:09.55,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}告別之後　一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:15.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}迎來重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:26.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}想躺在那綠色的草坪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:37.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}和動物們一起悠閒自得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:45.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}今天喜事多…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是電磁場光共振部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如其名  進行狙擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已確認衛星兵器被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密已脫離戰鬥區域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是多虧了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Celestial Being的戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E探測器有反應  是敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們得為擊落Memento Mori贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:12.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#14  聽到歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已查明同步衛星軌道上發生的爆炸事故
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起因是反聯邦勢力的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對應日益猖獗的恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦議會將直接管理聯邦軍和獨立治安維持部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全世界規模進行防衛網的強化…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento Mori被擊落了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙的卡塔隆大部分都被消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現統一世界的永久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都必須消滅Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果繼續容忍他們的存在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府勢力就有重新取得優勢的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匯合地點  應該是在這附近的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的GN粒子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi  好久不見了  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼蒂！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成個好男人了啊  妮娜很動心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  等一下啊  剛才不是才幫了你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你們的船貌似落到地球上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把戰鬥資料傳送給你  看了的話連行蹤也… 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…怎麼這麼急啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是這麼性急  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了  被甩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是吹的什麼風啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然特地到中東來見我 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想要傳達給在軍隊裡擔任監查任務的你的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊中有人在策劃發動政變
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我認為對聯邦政府的政策持反感態度的人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然會搞政變…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府已經成了A-LAWS的傀儡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要讓世人們清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O…O-Raizer呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力？  什麼時候到地上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥呀！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對監視用光學迷彩已恢復  展開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  讓OO-Raizer啟動  擊退了拉格朗治3的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從A-LAWS那知道了聯邦使用衛星兵器的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並前往執行破壞任務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然順利幹掉了  但是卻受到敵人的奇襲而落到大氣圈內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地上迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還與刹那駕駛的OO-Raizer走散了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是慘到家了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛  大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星兵器已經被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在用盡GN粒子的時候受到的奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外敵人的部隊還投入了新型MA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有利用船中彈的衝擊加速
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並利用煙霧偽裝  將船體降落到地上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些皇·李·諾瑞加帶來的轉機的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們早就被幹掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條命沒丟就該謝天謝地了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那托勒密的情況呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然引擎沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但航行系統  武器控制  通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探測器之類的損傷嚴重…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…  如果這種時候被敵人襲擊的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  我把吃的拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這也太散漫了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓瑪麗小姐參加戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且瑪麗也接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…  請不要讓這種事再發生第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星兵器雖然被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這邊損傷也不小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的情況恐怕是要借用支部的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟誰打電話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些俗事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼A-LAWS能那麼準確的掌握普特利麥奧斯的位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:09:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  利塔娜小姐是在懷疑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  只是有這個疑問而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還有  叫我亞琉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…  那麼叫我萊爾就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾·迪蘭地  是我的本名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密的反應…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這就是衛星兵器的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也都是改革者計劃之下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…  那傢伙為什麼會在這裡！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…  跟過來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍的一部分在策劃著政變！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎？池田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報來源是我做記者時的老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個值得信賴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於無法忍受A-LAWS的惡行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政變派想要跟我們進行接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會談場所似乎是指定在中東的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  克勞斯  也可能是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意相信想要糾正聯邦的惡政的他們的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且想要回應他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像是瑪麗娜公主把孩子們的話搜集起來寫的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況還能唱歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…  到底想到哪兒去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個方向是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克魯吉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底準備做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克魯吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已經是克魯吉斯的小哥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然跑到改革者那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  傭兵只要有人雇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是看報酬挑工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的戰鬥是沒有意義的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊  不過你應該理解不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是帶了個想見你的人來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的雇主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫李本茲  李本茲·阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了  刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索蘭·伊布拉希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  對你來說跟我是初次見面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對我來說可不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在十一年前就見過你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人類之間相互爭鬥而不得自拔的戰場上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個拼命躲避著的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從MS的駕駛艙裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難  難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在O-Gundam裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次武力介入是O-Gundam的性能測試
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然為了保密  在場的所有人原本都應該處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我卻救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為注視著O-Gundam…注視著我的你那雙眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我留下很深的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此  通過吠陀推薦你成為Gundam Meister的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我道謝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的使命已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是時候該還給我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原本就是該由我搭乘的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆  我的生存價值就是戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙  有兩台未確認的MS從不同方向過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  讓阿里路亞和特瑞亞出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭…瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  我們的位置被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee  特瑞亞·埃德  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios  阿里路亞·哈普提茲姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始迎擊行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀的狀況…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破綻！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑那種身體狀況還能有這種動作…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊  那傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊型  不會讓你射擊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有哈里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大氣層內還得計算對方的機動性啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你有吠陀的輔助！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞·埃德  你可是改革者！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來跟我們一起貫徹使命！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…改革者的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭在蔓延…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想  要是你們的歌能傳達給大家就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得唱出來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我只能做到這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要做到這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同類相殘雖不忍目睹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也有不得不為之的使命！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相讓的東西我們也有！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關閉了Field？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM嗎  就憑這種程度！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟Nadleeh那時候不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是以自己的意志  展現出這個姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seraphim Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Seraphim:和Seravee一樣，是熾天使的另一種說法）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想對同類刀刃相向嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！我是人類！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林格！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林格·斯塔比提！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  特瑞亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  得寸進尺…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯  是MS！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:19:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來為我們護航嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就算是人質了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下你就無法出手…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了…歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:57.71,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}なくす事が拾うためなら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:03.30,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}別れるのは出逢うため
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:08.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}「さようなら」のあとには　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:14.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}「こんにちは」と出逢うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:25.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}緑色芝生に寝ころんでいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:36.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}動物も一緒にゴロゴロしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:48.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}今日は良い事がたくさんあったから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:59.20,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明日も良い事がたくさんあるように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:04.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}お日様出て　夕日きれいで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:10.25,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}星に願い明日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:15.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}どうして行っちゃうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:21.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}一緒に帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:57.71,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}若丟棄是為了撿回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:03.30,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}那分別就是為了相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:08.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}告別之後　一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:14.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}迎來重逢
